data.description: Welcome to this move-in ready duplex located on Mill Pond in the charming town of Laurel, DE. This spacious and well-maintained home offers three bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms, providing ample space for comfortable living.  Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The traditional concept layout seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating a perfect space for entertaining family and friends. The kitchen features modern appliances and ample cabinet space.  The 1st floor owner bedroom boasts an ensuite bathroom, providing a private retreat for relaxation. Upstairs, you'll find the two generously sized bedrooms, each offering plenty of natural light and closet space.   Enjoy the serene views of Mill Pond from your backyard, where you can unwind and appreciate the peaceful surroundings. The low-maintenance yard allows for more time to relax and enjoy the outdoors.  Conveniently located in Laurel, DE, this duplex offers easy access to local amenities, schools, shopping centers, and dining options. With its move-in ready condition, you can settle in quickly and start enjoying the comforts of your new home.  Recent upgrades: Kitchen Countertops and Sink, New Windows.  HVAC replaced in 2019, Fenced Yard.  Bring your electric boat or kayak and enjoy Mill Pond in your back yard.  A John Boat with Electric Motor and all accessories will be included in this sale.  Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a beautiful duplex on Mill Pond in Laurel, DE. Schedule a showing today and experience the charm and convenience this home has to offer.  This property has $128K assumable loan @ 3.2%
